          "date": "2014-02-20 12:00:56.000000000",
          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-4584 ptlrpc: force to replay open upon truncate",
        "message": "LU-4584 ptlrpc: force to replay open upon truncate\n\nIf a truncate occurs during Server reply for an open request, it\nis likely to occur due to embedded (large!) layout. And thus, the\nrequest must be replayed otherwise layout will be locked twice on\nServer side, finally causing Client eviction since it will only\ncancel once upon Blocking-AST.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I74f5cf816b390920e611ce231b8c309c35ad04f9\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_4"
    }
